1
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:15,840
Are you really Yu?

2
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:20,480
I once told a girl

3
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:24,600
that I would make her the happiest person in the world.

4
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:27,000
Until this vow is fulfilled,

5
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,040
I cannot show her my true face.

6
00:00:32,479 --> 00:00:33,340
This is for you.

7
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:36,640
What is this?

8
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:39,440
Dandian is my most precious thing.

9
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:41,560
I have been hiding it

10
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,690
so that the Gu family wouldn't find it.

11
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,200
Then why did you give it to me?

12
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:49,880
Because right now, you are the most precious to me.

13
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,040
What's wrong?

14
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:59,760
You seem preoccupied.

15
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:02,920
Yun, I, Gu Chengyu, swear to heaven

16
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:06,320
that one day you will become the happiest person in the world.

17
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,289
But you don't need to worry.

18
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,640
This vow will be fulfilled soon.

19
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,660
About those childhood memories,

20
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,720
only Ayu and I know.

21
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,039
If he really is Ayu,

22
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,759
why does he feel so unfamiliar to me?

23
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,800
This is a forbidden area.

24
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,120
Who let you in?

25
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,600
I let you go,

26
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,360
not to give you freedom.

27
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:10,080
If you dare approach this Yuyun tree again,

28
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:11,680
you will die.

29
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,760
Yuyun Tree.

30
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,450
How could he know about the Yuyun Tree?

31
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:20,840
I thought of a name for it.

32
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:23,360
Let's call it the Yuyun Tree.

33
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:28,040
Yu represents you, and Yun represents me.

34
00:02:57,160 --> 00:03:00,600
The Yuyun Tree is a secret between Gu Chengyu and me.

35
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,080
How could Mo Yu know about it?

36
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,400
Could he be...

37
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,480
But Su Cheng has the jade pendant,

38
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:11,210
and knows about our childhood.

39
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:20,520
There can't possibly be two Gu Chengyus in this world.

40
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,130
There must be a conspiracy.

41
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:33,600
Mo Yu. Su Cheng.

42
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,210
The mysterious person.

43
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:40,400
What is the relationship between them?

44
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,200
I want revenge.

45
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,400
I want to kill Gu Licheng and his wife right now.

46
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,360
Didn't I tell you to wait?

47
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,240
Now is not the time.

48
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,880
I'm just informing you.

49
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:57,000
If you want the Minister of Revenue,

50
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,440
you only have one chance.

51
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,200
Whether you can seize it

52
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,000
is up to you.

53
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,000
Since you insist,

54
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,160
I'll help you once.

55
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,920
But this plan

56
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,600
requires using someone.

57
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,200
Why are you here?

58
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,240
A letter of divorce.

59
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,960
I know you don't want to marry me,

60
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:38,040
but I have a favor to ask now.

61
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,640
If you are willing to help me,

62
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,080
after it's done,

63
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,360
I will give you complete freedom.

64
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:50,680
What exactly do you want me to help you with?

65
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,800
To deal with Gu Licheng and his wife.

66
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:03,240
You mean you want them to compete fairly?

67
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,240
Exactly.

68
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:08,400
Although Gu Licheng and Su Cheng are both Vice Ministers of Revenue,

69
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:11,160
there is only one person in charge of the rock oil trade between our countries.

70
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,960
That is the Minister of Revenue.

71
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,760
Instead of letting the Emperor of Great Jin decide,

72
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:18,040
it's better for us to take the initiative.

73
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,440
But in a fair competition,

74
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,360
how can we have the initiative?

75
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,690
Think about it, Mother.

76
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:24,200
If we propose a candidate directly,

77
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:26,240
the Emperor of Great Jin will definitely refuse.

78
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,400
But if we suggest a fair competition,

79
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:30,720
the Emperor will have nothing to say.

80
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,530
No matter who wins between the two of them,

81
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:36,120
they will be grateful for your promotion, Mother.

82
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:36,880
In the future,

83
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:38,400
as long as we win them over,

84
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:41,200
we can hold more initiative in the trade.

85
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:45,000
Alright. I'll go talk to the Emperor of Great Jin now.

86
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:45,960
But my dear,

87
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:49,600
why are you suddenly so interested in state affairs?

88
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,720
Although I married into Great Jin,

89
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,920
I will always be the Princess of Beidi.

90
00:05:57,920 --> 00:06:02,380
Naturally, I want to fight for more benefits for our country and for you, Mother.

91
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,920
I have summoned you here today

92
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:08,480
because His Majesty of Beidi and I have agreed

93
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,120
that you two will compete fairly

94
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,560
for the position of Minister of Revenue,

95
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,680
to be responsible for the trade between our two nations.

96
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,840
I obey your command.

97
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,410
However, I believe that

98
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,040
since you will be responsible for bilateral trade,

99
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:21,480
apart from having solid professional skills and being meticulous,

100
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,480
you also need to be tactful

101
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,400
to win the favor of both nations.

102
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:28,800
Therefore, by organizing the alliance banquet,

103
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,840
you two will compete fairly.

104
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,960
Whoever organizes it better

105
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,020
will become the Minister of Revenue.

106
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:37,600
Your Majesty of Northern Di, what do you think?

107
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:40,440
Very well. It is decided then.

108
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,920
Mo Yu,

109
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,040
I did what you asked me to do.

110
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,720
Even though I do not know what you want to do,

111
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,680
I also have my own backup plan.

112
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:55,520
I heard you still have not gained Mo Yu's trust.

113
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,840
Mo Yu is suspicious by nature,

114
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,000
temperamental,

115
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,560
and there are villains getting in the way.

116
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,680
No need to explain.

117
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,800
I only want results.

118
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:08,760
I still need his prestige to intimidate enemy countries.

119
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:12,600
He thinks he holds the power of both the military and finance.

120
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:16,080
But I placed the two of you by his side

121
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:19,000
just to monitor his every move.

122
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,680
If he has any intentions of rebellion,

123
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:23,200
we must strike first

124
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,600
and get rid of him.

125
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,480
Your Majesty is wise.

126
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,330
Step forward, my minister.

127
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,320
My minister,

128
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,560
this last chance,

129
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,640
it is truly for you

130
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:42,560
that I lowered its difficulty to the minimum.

131
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:47,720
If you cannot even organize a small banquet well,

132
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:56,040
then I will have to support Su Cheng and give up on you.

133
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,800
I will definitely do my best.

134
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,650
Bo Baorui

135
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,460
Zhong Xiaqiang

136
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:16,660
Peng Yin

137
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,080
Zijian Qiangqipin Peng Yin

138
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,100
Zijian Qiangqipin

139
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,360
Quan Xuhang

140
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,020
Quan Xuhang

141
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:19,680
Quan Yulong

142
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,340
Quan Yulong

143
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,440
Licheng Lefei

144
